OL,3,CMaisie Peters among artists to preform
OL,4,Cat O2 for 20th anniversary
OL,6,FLondon's O2 will mark its 20th
OL,7,Fanniversary with series of residencies
OL,8,Fand one-off special performances next
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FThe music and entertainment venue
OL,12,Fofficially opened to the public on
OL,13,FJune 24, 2007, which was followed by a
OL,14,Fconcert from rock band Bon Jovi.
OL,16,FThroughout 2027, the anniversary shows
OL,17,Fwill bring together a line-up of
OL,18,Fartists spanning rising stars to
OL,19,Fglobal icons across a range of genres.
