OL,3,CMaisie Peters among artists to preform
OL,4,Cat O2 for 20th anniversary
OL,6,FBritish singer-songwriter, Maisie
OL,7,FPeters, has been confirmed as the
OL,8,Ffirst headliner for the anniversary
OL,9,Fevents.
OL,11,FThe gig will be her debut headline
OL,12,Fshow at The O2 on Saturday 8 May 2027.
OL,14,FThe 25-year-old singer said: "Being
OL,15,Fthe first artist announced for The
OL,16,FO2's 20th birthday celebration is
OL,17,Fhonestly such an honour.
OL,26,@vD@^OU
