PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778847105
OL,3,CMaisie Peters among artists to preform
OL,4,Cat O2 for 20th anniversary
OL,6,F"I've been a fan of the venue for as
OL,7,Flong as I can remember and have
OL,8,Fwatched so many shows there, so
OL,9,Fgetting to step onto that stage for my
OL,10,Fown headline show feels like a real
OL,11,Fdream come true.
OL,13,F"The O2 holds so many iconic moments,
OL,14,Fand to be part of the very start of
OL,15,Fits next chapter makes this moment
OL,16,Feven more special and I can't wait to
OL,17,Fshare it with my fans." said Maisie
OL,18,FPeters.
OL,26,@yD@WO]
