OL,3,CMaisie Peters among artists to preform
OL,4,Cat O2 for 20th anniversary
OL,6,FMore than 3,000 shows have been
OL,7,Fperformed at the O2 since it's opening
OL,8,Fwhile also welcoming more than a 100
OL,9,Fmillion visitors.
OL,11,FSteve Sayer, Senior Vice President and
OL,12,FGeneral Manager of The O2 said: "Our
OL,13,Fbirthday celebrations are about
OL,14,Freflecting on our success and legacy
OL,15,Fwhilst continuing to look firmly to
OL,16,Fthe future.
OL,18,F"Bringing together iconic acts
OL,19,Falongside the next generation of
OL,20,Ftalent is central to that vision."
OL,26,@tD@aOU
