OL,3,CMaisie Peters among artists to preform
OL,4,Cat O2 for 20th anniversary
OL,6,FThe O2 is primarily used for hosting
OL,7,Fmajor live music concerts, sports
OL,8,Fevents, comedy shows, and awards
OL,9,Fceremonies, hosting over 200 events
OL,10,Fannually.
OL,12,FGareth Griffiths, Virgin Media O2
OL,13,Fsaid: "We couldn't be prouder of our
OL,14,Fpartnership with AEG and everything we
OL,15,Fhave achieved together at The O2 in
OL,16,FLondon ` countless memories made at
OL,17,Fshows which have shaped music and
OL,18,Fentertainment as we know it, putting
OL,19,Fthe fan at the centre of the
OL,20,Fexperience every step of the way.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
